room_type¶

In [12]:
tab = pandas.concat(
    [
        pandas.crosstab(data["room_type"], "#"),
        (pandas.crosstab(data["room_type"], "%", normalize = True) * 100).round(2)

    axis = 1).sort_values("#", ascending = False)
